org.polarsys.chess.chessmlprofile.Predictability.ARINCComponentModel

Interface ARINCFunction

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ARINCFunctionImpl

    public interface ARINCFunction
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'ARINC Function'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Base Operation
    • Base Comment
    • Followed By
    • Rate Divider
    See Also:
    ARINCComponentModelPackage.getARINCFunction()
